Package: typethis
Title: Type Safety and Validation for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("TypeThis Team", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides comprehensive type safety and validation for R, similar to
    Python's mypy and pydantic. Includes runtime type checking, typed functions,
    validators, and typed data models with automatic validation. Helps catch type
    errors early and write more robust R code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Imports:
    methods
URL: https://github.com/fabiandistler/typethis
BugReports: https://github.com/fabiandistler/typethis/issues
